snippet.title: Unbodied - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Unbodied is a small adventure full of magic, puzzles, and strange characters. Explore the entire cemetery, get your magic wand, and find all the spells that will help you progress. Don't forget to beat up the powerful wizard who stole your body.

Coming 16 August on Steam, Itch.io and Gamejolt.
